cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.DS, cs.PL

The paper involves mechanical reasoning and analysis of infinite games, which are typically studied in the field of logic (cs.LO). The use of proof assistant Coq also suggests a focus on formal methods and automated reasoning, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also deals with game theory (cs.GT) and the analysis of extensive form games, which is a subfield of decision theory and optimization (cs.DS). Finally, the paper involves the use of programming languages and formal verification, which is related to programming languages and compilers (cs.PL).
